David Wolfe (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Wolfe_(actor) 0 David Wolfe, aka Dave Wolfe (March 1, 1915 - September 23, 1994) of New York City was an American film actor from 1949 to 1954. After his acting career, he was the romantic partner of American Broadway showman Tommy Tune.
